Package blackjack

package blackjack
  • Class
    Description
    Blackjack
    The class where everything runs.
    Card
    Represents a single playing card in a standard 52-card deck.
    Card.Suit
    Enumeration representing the four suits of a standard deck.
    Deck
    Represents a standard deck of playing cards used in a Blackjack game.
    FileManager
    Handles reading from and writing to a local file that stores the highest profit achieved in a Blackjack game session.
    Game
    The Game class represents a single game of Blackjack.
    Gui
    The graphical user interface of the game
    Hand
    Represents a player's or dealer's hand in a game of Blackjack.
